# Flowmate environment variables.
#
# v1 runs against the local Supabase stack (`supabase start`). Copy this file to
# `.env` and fill in the values printed by `supabase start`.
#
# The local-Supabase wiring (the typed client in `lib/data/` and the concrete
# variable set) lands in issue #3; until then this stub documents the contract:
# every variable the project reads is listed here, with no secrets committed.

# EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
